WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.072
The world of work is undergoing a profound transformation driven

00:00:04.072 --> 00:00:08.144
by Artificial Intelligence. We are moving into the era of

00:00:08.144 --> 00:00:12.216
Agentic AI, where AI systems act autonomously within multistep workflows.

00:00:12.216 --> 00:00:16.288
Your mandate is no longer managing linear tasks; it is

00:00:16.288 --> 00:00:20.360
redesigning entire workflows to orchestrate human-AI symbiosis.
